\frac{dy}{dx} = x^2 + y^2, \\ y(0) = 0
D:|x|,|y|\le 1
f(x,y)=x^2+y^2\le 2=M.
 \lvert x\rvert\le\min\left\{a,b/M\right\}=\min\left\{1,1/2\right\}=1/2. 
